вЌќ Builds the hand-crafted binary fixtures for ParseEXIF tests, with no
вЌќ external tool or library dependency. Run once with:
вЌќ   dyalogscript apl-service/tests/fixtures/exif/generate_fixtures.apls
вЌќ and check the resulting files into git alongside this script.
вЌќ
вЌќ TIFF entry/rational builders are dyadic (tag type count) Entry valueBytes
вЌќ and numerator Rational denominator, never bundling a scalar tuple with a
вЌќ vector via bare strand notation - that silently nests the result (mixing
вЌќ scalar and vector items in one strand forces the vector item to stay
вЌќ boxed) and produces a corrupt, non-flat byte array.

Dirв†ђ(вЉѓ1 вЋ•NPARTS''),'apl-service/tests/fixtures/exif'

EncNв†ђ{вЊЅ(вЌєвЌґ256)вЉ¤вЌµ}           вЌќ вЌє bytes, little-endian, of value вЌµ
BE2в†ђ{(2вЌґ256)вЉ¤вЌµ}               вЌќ 2 bytes, big-endian (JPEG segment length only)
Pad4в†ђ{4в†‘вЌµ,4вЌґ0}                 вЌќ left-justify bytes in a 4-byte field, zero-padded
Str0в†ђ{(вЋ•UCS вЌµ),0}              вЌќ ASCII bytes + NUL terminator
Entryв†ђ{(2 EncN вЌє[1]),(2 EncN вЌє[2]),(4 EncN вЌє[3]),Pad4 вЌµ}   вЌќ (tag type count) Entry valueOrOffsetBytes
Rationalв†ђ{(4 EncN вЌє),4 EncN вЌµ}                              вЌќ numerator Rational denominator -> 8 bytes
ToSignedв†ђ{вЌµ-256Г—вЌµ>127}         вЌќ 0-255 -> the -128..127 domain вЋ•NAPPEND type 83 expects

WrapJPEGв†ђ{                     вЌќ SOI, one APP1 segment holding 'Exif\0\0'+вЌµ, EOI
    exifHeaderв†ђ(вЋ•UCS'Exif'),0 0   вЌќ the fixed 6-byte 'Exif\0\0' APP1 identifier, not a TIFF ASCII field
    lenв†ђ2+(в‰ўexifHeader)+в‰ўвЌµ
    (255 216 255 225),(BE2 len),exifHeader,вЌµ,255 217
}

вЌќ A bare (unassigned) non-last statement in a dfn immediately returns its
вЌќ value and ends the function - every intermediate statement here must be
вЌќ assigned, even when its value is unused, or вЋ•NUNTIE below never runs.
WriteBytesв†ђ{
    tieв†ђвЌє(вЋ•NCREATEвЌ 'IfExists' 'Replace')0
    writtenв†ђ(ToSigned вЌµ)вЋ•NAPPEND tie 83
    вЋ•NUNTIE tie
}

вЌќ ---- TIFF blob layout (all offsets relative to the TIFF header's first byte) ----
tiffHeaderLenв†ђ8
ifd0Offsetв†ђtiffHeaderLen
nIfd0в†ђ5
ifd0TableLenв†ђ2+(12Г—nIfd0)+4        вЌќ count(2) + entries(12 each) + next-IFD(4)
ifd0ExtraOffsetв†ђifd0Offset+ifd0TableLen

makeBytesв†ђStr0'Canon'
modelBytesв†ђStr0'EOS R5'
makeOffsetв†ђifd0ExtraOffset
modelOffsetв†ђmakeOffset+в‰ўmakeBytes
ifd0ExtraLenв†ђ(в‰ўmakeBytes)+в‰ўmodelBytes
exifIFDOffsetв†ђifd0ExtraOffset+ifd0ExtraLen

nExifв†ђ3
exifTableLenв†ђ2+(12Г—nExif)+4
exifExtraOffsetв†ђexifIFDOffset+exifTableLen
dtoBytesв†ђStr0'2026:06:30 14:22:05'
dtoOffsetв†ђexifExtraOffset
exifExtraLenв†ђв‰ўdtoBytes
gpsIFDOffsetв†ђexifExtraOffset+exifExtraLen

nGpsв†ђ4
gpsTableLenв†ђ2+(12Г—nGps)+4
gpsExtraOffsetв†ђgpsIFDOffset+gpsTableLen
latBytesв†ђ(37 Rational 1),(46 Rational 1),30 Rational 1
latOffsetв†ђgpsExtraOffset
longBytesв†ђ(122 Rational 1),(25 Rational 1),6 Rational 1
longOffsetв†ђlatOffset+в‰ўlatBytes

ifd0Entriesв†ђ((271 2(в‰ўmakeBytes))Entry(4 EncN makeOffset)),((272 2(в‰ўmodelBytes))Entry(4 EncN modelOffset)),((274 3 1)Entry(Pad4 2 EncN 1)),((34665 4 1)Entry(4 EncN exifIFDOffset)),(34853 4 1)Entry(4 EncN gpsIFDOffset)
ifd0Tableв†ђ(2 EncN nIfd0),ifd0Entries,4 EncN 0
ifd0Extraв†ђmakeBytes,modelBytes

exifEntriesв†ђ((36867 2(в‰ўdtoBytes))Entry(4 EncN dtoOffset)),((40962 4 1)Entry(Pad4 4 EncN 4032)),(40963 4 1)Entry(Pad4 4 EncN 3024)
exifTableв†ђ(2 EncN nExif),exifEntries,4 EncN 0
exifExtraв†ђdtoBytes

gpsEntriesв†ђ((1 2 2)Entry(Pad4 Str0'N')),((2 5 3)Entry(4 EncN latOffset)),((3 2 2)Entry(Pad4 Str0'W')),(4 5 3)Entry(4 EncN longOffset)
gpsTableв†ђ(2 EncN nGps),gpsEntries,4 EncN 0
gpsExtraв†ђlatBytes,longBytes

tiffHeaderв†ђ(вЋ•UCS'II'),(2 EncN 42),4 EncN ifd0Offset
tiffв†ђtiffHeader,ifd0Table,ifd0Extra,exifTable,exifExtra,gpsTable,gpsExtra

вЌќ ---- Corrupted TIFF variants, built by mutating exact known byte ranges of `tiff` ----

вЌќ malformed_tiff_header: byte-order marker is neither 'II' nor 'MM'
tiffBadHeaderв†ђtiff
tiffBadHeader[1 2]в†ђ90 90

вЌќ out_of_bounds_ifd0: Model's (IFD0 entry 2) value/offset field points past EOF
modelEntryBaseв†ђifd0Offset+2+12Г—2-1
tiffOOBв†ђtiff
tiffOOB[modelEntryBase+8+вЌі4]в†ђ4 EncN 5000

вЌќ zero_denominator_gps: GPSLatitude's first rational (degrees) has denominator 0
tiffZeroDenomв†ђtiff
tiffZeroDenom[latOffset+4+вЌі4]в†ђ4 EncN 0

вЌќ ---- Assemble the JPEG-wrapped fixtures ----
withExifв†ђWrapJPEG tiff
malformedHeaderв†ђWrapJPEG tiffBadHeader
outOfBoundsIfd0в†ђWrapJPEG tiffOOB
zeroDenomGpsв†ђWrapJPEG tiffZeroDenom

noExifв†ђ255 216 255 218 0 4 0 0 255 217   вЌќ SOI, then SOS immediately (no APP1), EOI
notAnImageв†ђ137 80 78 71 13 10 26 10 0 0 0 0   вЌќ PNG signature, not a JPEG

вЌќ corrupt_truncated: with_exif cut mid-IFD0 (TIFF header + count + first two entries only)
truncateAtв†ђ12+ifd0Offset+2+24     вЌќ 12 = SOI+APP1marker+len+'Exif00' prefix before the TIFF blob
corruptTruncatedв†ђtruncateAtв†‘withExif

вЋ•в†ђ'with_exif length ',(вЌ•в‰ўwithExif),' depth ',вЌ•в‰ЎwithExif
вЋ•в†ђ'corrupt_truncated length ',вЌ•в‰ўcorruptTruncated

(Dir,'/with_exif.jpg')WriteBytes withExif
(Dir,'/no_exif.jpg')WriteBytes noExif
(Dir,'/not_an_image.png')WriteBytes notAnImage
(Dir,'/corrupt_truncated.jpg')WriteBytes corruptTruncated
(Dir,'/malformed_tiff_header.jpg')WriteBytes malformedHeader
(Dir,'/out_of_bounds_ifd0.jpg')WriteBytes outOfBoundsIfd0
(Dir,'/zero_denominator_gps.jpg')WriteBytes zeroDenomGps

вЋ•в†ђ'wrote 7 fixtures to ',Dir

вЌќ ---- Self-check: independent decode of with_exif.jpg from disk ----
DecNв†ђ{256вЉҐвЊЅвЌµ}
tieв†ђвЉѓ(Dir,'/with_exif.jpg')вЋ•NTIE 0
rawв†ђ256|вЋ•NREAD tie 83 100000
вЋ•NUNTIE tie

вЌќ direct sliding-window search, small file so a simple loop is fine
tiffStartInFileв†ђВЇ1
:For p :In вЌі(в‰ўraw)-5
    :If (6в†‘pв†“raw)в‰Ў(вЋ•UCS'Exif'),0 0
        tiffStartInFileв†ђp+6
        :Leave
    :EndIf
:EndFor
вЋ•в†ђ'tiff blob starts at file offset ',вЌ•tiffStartInFile

rtiffв†ђtiffStartInFileв†“raw
decodedIfd0Offв†ђDecN rtiff[2+2+вЌі4]
nв†ђDecN rtiff[decodedIfd0Off+1 2]
вЋ•в†ђ'decoded IFD0 entry count from disk = ',вЌ•n

ValAtв†ђ{baseв†ђdecodedIfd0Off+2+12Г—вЌµ-1 в‹„ rtiff[base+8+вЌі4]}
CountAtв†ђ{baseв†ђdecodedIfd0Off+2+12Г—вЌµ-1 в‹„ DecN rtiff[base+4+вЌі4]}
mCntв†ђCountAt 1 в‹„ mOffв†ђDecN ValAt 1
вЋ•в†ђ'Make (from disk) = ',вЋ•UCS rtiff[mOff+вЌіmCnt-1]

вЋ•OFF
